Package: gplite
Title: Lightweight interface to the most common Gaussian process models
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Juho", "Piironen", role = c("cre", "aut"), email = "juho.t.piironen@gmail.com"))
Description: Implements a lightweight interface to type-II maximum likelihood and Markov chain Monte Carlo
inference for Gaussian Process (GP) models using Stan. New observation models and covariance functions
are easy to add.
Depends: 
  R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: 
  rstan
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
